'一个程序运行时会产生很多信息，在Linux中用于存放此类信息的文件，叫做日志。MySQL中根据信息的不同，所记录的日志分为查询日志、慢查询日志、错误日志、二进制日志、中继日志和事务日志。\r'),(797,168,'description_value','数据库按照是否使用关系表组织可以分为关系型数据库和非关系型数据库，而MySQL属于关系型数据库大家庭中的一员。\r'),(798,168,'keywords_value',''),(799,167,'description_value','日志主要包括系统日志、应用程序日志和安全日志。系统运维和开发人员可以通过日志了解服务器软硬件信息、检查配置过程中的错误及错误发生的原因。经常分析日志可以了解服务器的负荷，性能安全性，从而及时采取措施纠正错误。\r'),(800,167,'keywords_value',''),(801,167,'_edit_lock','1464569210:1'),(802,167,'_edit_last','1'),(808,42,'views','11'),(804,167,'views','41'),(811,104,'views','13'),(822,176,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:686;s:6:\"height\";i:237;s:4:\"file\";s:43:\"2016/05/wxtblog.com_2016-05-29_14-01-29.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:43:\"wxtblog.com_2016-05-29_14-01-29-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:43:\"wxtblog.com_2016-05-29_14-01-29-300x104.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:104;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:43:\"wxtblog.com_2016-05-29_14-01-29-280x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:280;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(823,175,'_edit_last','1'),(826,175,'views','32'),(832,177,'description_value','Salt安装以及targeting\r'),(833,177,'keywords_value',''),(834,177,'_edit_lock','1464939805:1'),(835,177,'_edit_last','1'),(836,178,'_wp_attached_file','2016/05/1.png'),(837,178,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:571;s:6:\"height\";i:118;s:4:\"file\";s:13:\"2016/05/1.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:13:\"1-150x118.png\";s:5:\"wid